name: Product 1

header.title: Product 1
header.subTitle: Three Leaf Clover, symbolizes good luck and fortune in many cultures.

guide.water: Allow the soil to dry out completely before watering.
guide.tips: Gently insert a toothpick into the soil to determine if your plant needs watering.
